"title": "5426: news",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5426: news",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Information on significant or recent events conveyed through a variety of official or unofficial means. The ministry of Jesus Christ centred on the good news of the kingdom. The Greek word for “gospel” means “good news”.</p>\n<h2>Political news reported by official and self-appointed messengers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam31:8-1Sam31:9\">1SA 31:8–31:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:1-2Sam1:10\">2SA 1:1–1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:13\">2SA 15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:19-2Sam18:32\">2SA 18:19–18:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:8-2Kgs7:11\">2KI 7:8–7:11</a></p>\n<h2>Personal news conveyed through friends, relatives and by letter</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:7-Col4:9\">COL 4:7–4:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:11-Gen29:13\">GEN 29:11–29:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:19-Phil2:20\">PHP 2:19–2:20</a></p>\n<h2>Divine news announced by angels</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:19\">LUK 1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:1\">GEN 19:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:26-Luke1:33\">LUK 1:26–1:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:8-Luke2:12\">LUK 2:8–2:12</a></p>\n<h2>The effect of good news</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:25\">PRO 25:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:16\">GEN 45:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:30\">PRO 15:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:18-Nah3:19\">NAM 3:18–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:51-John4:53\">JHN 4:51–4:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:6-1Thess3:10\">1TH 3:6–3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Reactions to bad news</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:23\">JER 49:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:12-1Sam4:22\">1SA 4:12–4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:10\">2SA 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:14-Job1:21\">JOB 1:14–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:1-Jonah3:10\">JON 3:1–3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:1-John11:6\">JHN 11:1–11:6</a></p>\n<h2>The good news of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Foretold</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:17\">NUM 24:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:14\">ISA 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:7\">ISA 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3-Isa53:12\">ISA 53:3–53:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:3\">ISA 61:1–61:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:2\">MIC 5:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech11:12-Zech11:13\">ZEC 11:12–11:13</a></p>\n<h3>Announced and demonstrated by Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:23\">MAT 4:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:5\">MAT 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:17-Luke4:19\">LUK 4:17–4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:43\">LUK 4:43</a></p>\n<h3>Proclaimed by apostles and preachers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:21\">ACT 14:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:15\">MRK 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:14-Rom10:15\">ROM 10:14–10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:11\">2TI 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>Spread by word of mouth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:19-Acts11:20\">ACT 11:19–11:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:24\">MAT 4:24</a></p>\n<h3>Receiving the good news</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:12\">ACT 8:12</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Rejecting the good news</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:16\">ROM 10:16</a></strong></p>",
